pi_A <- 0.22
pi_B <- 0.18
theta_true <- pi_A - pi_B

x_A <- rbinom(n_A, size = 1, prob = pi_A)
x_B <- rbinom(n_B, size = 1, prob = pi_B)

theta_hat <- mean(x_A) - mean(x_B)

tibble(
  group = c("A", "B"),
  signup_rate = c(mean(x_A), mean(x_B))
)
The observed estimate from this simulated dataset is:
